<D>__{no thanks, i got a pie to eat.}
<A>__{hilly spins around and sees the pie.}
<C>__{hilly}
<D>__{you throw that pie away right now!}
<C>__{missus walters}
<D>__{i spent good money on this. won it just for you...}
<C>__{hilly}
<D>__{you?! you signed me up?}
<A>__{missus walters steps up to hilly.}
<C>__{missus walters}
<D>__{i may have trouble remembering my own name and what country i live in. but there's two things i can't seem to forget. that my own daughter threw me in a nursing home...and that she ate minny's shit.}
<A>__{missus walters winks at hilly and ambles to a waiting taxi cab.}
